claim.claim-text:
A compound according to claim 1 or 2, said compound selected form the group comprised of:
- 3-(4-methoxyphenyl)-5-propyl-furo[3,2-g]chromen-7-one;
- 3-(4-methoxyphenyl)-5,6-dimethyl-furo[3,2-g]chromen-7-one;
- 5-butyl-3-(4-methoxyphenyl)furo[3,2-g]chromen-7-one.

Use of a compound as a medicament, said compound selected form the group comprised of:
- 3-(4-methoxyphenyl)-5-propyl-furo[3,2-g]chromen-7-one;
- 3-(4-methoxyphenyl)-5,6-dimethyl-furo[3,2-g]chromen-7-one;
- 5-butyl-3-(4-methoxyphenyl)furo[3,2-g]chromen-7-one.
